edu.rit.draw.item

Class SolidOutline

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.draw.item.SolidOutline
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Outline, Externalizable, Serializable

    public class SolidOutline
extends Object
implements Outline
    Class SolidOutline provides an object that outlines an area in a DrawingItem with a square-cornered solid stroke in a solid color.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
